        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Reducing Hereditary Cancer Act of </b><b>2022</b></p> <p>This bill provides for Medicare coverage of germline mutation testing for individuals with a personal or family history of a hereditary cancer gene mutation or suspected history of hereditary cancer, as well as for associated coverage of risk-reducing surgeries and screenings.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
